quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  43,34,"(Men wa…óayno kadi) e cuu…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, dame e nda…ó…óude ka …ìe so…ì…ìindoo"
  43,35,"e cu…óaari. Kono …óum fow wonaali, si wanaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko laakara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gom…óum…ìe …ìen"
  43,36,"Kala …óuurnii…óo e jantoore Hinaranko On, Men wuurta mo e seytanuuru, hara ko ndun woni ko o coowodata"
  43,37,"∆äin (awaseeji) non, ko sakkoray…ói …ìe e peewal ngal, haa ka …ìe sikkata hi…ìe feewi"
  43,38,"Haa si o aroyii e Amen, o wi'a: \"Ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa wo…ó…óirayno go…ó…óal fu…ó…óir…óe …óen …ói…ói wo…ó…óiri ! A bonii cinndadii…óo"
  43,39,"[∆äum] nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on too√±ii - wonnde ko ka lepte hawtu…óon"
  43,40,E ko an naninta faa…óu…óo maa fewnaa bum…óo e on won…óo e nder majjere …ìanngunde
  43,41,"Si Men aru ∆¥ettitude ma, haray ko Men yottotoo…ìe e ma…ì…ìe"
  43,42,"maa hara Men holle ko Men kammbirani …ìen kon, haray noon ko Men gaynoo…ìe fii ma…ì…ìe"
  43,43,"Jogito kon ko wahayinaa e maa…óa. Pellet, hi…óa jokki laawol focciingol"
  43,44,"Ndee non [Alqur'aanaare], ko nde teddungal maa an e yim…ìe maa …ìen. Aray nde lamndite…óon"
  43,45,"Lamndii e …ìen Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìe Men nulunoo ado maa, si Men wa…óuno ko wanaa Hinnaranke On, rewetee…ói goo"
  43,46,"Gom…óii Men immindinii Muusaa e Aayeeje Amen …óen, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun, o maaki: \"Ko mi Nulaa…óo Jey…óo tagu ngun"
  43,47,"Nde o addannoo…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen, e jaka yoo hi…ìe jala…ói"
